data.description: **SELLER TO OFFER A $10,000 CLOSING COST CREDIT FOR FULL PRICE OFFER** Home located in quite cul-de-sac with NO HOA and LOW property taxes! Move in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is a true gem. Inside you'll be greeted by vaulted ceilings with natural light. The living area is adorned with a stunning fireplace and the open concept kitchen is perfect for entertaining guests. One of the standout features of this property is the oversized 7500 square foot lot, providing ample space for all your outdoor activities with convenient RV parking. Relax all year round in the heated pool and spa, offering a luxurious retreat right in your backyard surrounded by the beauty of the desert landscape. The covered patio is an inviting extension of your living space, perfect for dining, morning coffees, or relaxing in your private sanctuary. Say goodbye to tedious yard work - this property boasts a low-maintenance, drought-resistant desert landscaping with a state-of-the-art drip system.
